headline: Is Uber Technologies (UBER) Share Price Missing The Mark After Strong Multi Year Gains
summary: If you are wondering whether Uber Technologies' current share price truly reflects its value, you are not alone. headline: How The Narrative Around Uber Technologies (UBER) Is Shifting With AV And AI Repricing
summary: Uber Technologies has just seen its fair value estimate nudged slightly lower, from about US$112.06 to about US$110.72 per share, reflecting a very modest recalibration rather than a wholesale rethink. The updated model threads a slightly higher discount rate of about 8.05% together with a very small adjustment to the long term revenue growth assumption, now about 14.60%, as analysts weigh both enthusiasm and caution around autonomous vehicles and AI.
